### **Basic Implementation**
This will calculate the raw score as the total number of matched n-grams between the prompt and pattern.

```csharp
class NGramScorer
{
    public int ComputeScore(IEnumerable<string> promptNGrams, IEnumerable<string> patternNGrams)
    {
        // Convert pattern n-grams to a HashSet for fast lookup
        var patternSet = new HashSet<string>(patternNGrams);
        int score = 0;

        // Iterate through prompt n-grams and count matches
        foreach (var nGram in promptNGrams)
        {
            if (patternSet.Contains(nGram))
            {
                score++;
            }
        }

        return score; // Return the raw score as the total number of matches
    }
}
```

